trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The AssemblyCollection class does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
trans-unit.target: AssemblyCollection 類別未參考任何基礎的組態檔中的實際項目。

trans-unit.source: It is a construct that allows access to the assembly information it contains.
trans-unit.target: 它是建構，可讓它包含的組件資訊的存取權。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Adds an <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo"></xref> object to the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> collection.
Adds an <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyInfo> object to the collection.
If the assembly object is not initialized with assembly information, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 如果組件物件未初始化的組件資訊，會擲回例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: If the assembly object already exists in the collection, the statement is ignored.
trans-unit.target: 如果集合中已經存在的組件物件，則會忽略陳述式。
